= Troubleshooting =
== incompatible with user-sysmaint-split ==
VeraCrypt has been reported to be incompatible with [[sysmaint|user-sysmaint-split]]. <ref>
https://forums.whonix.org/t/whonix-user-isolation-user-sysmaint-split-breaks-veracrypt-workflow/21629/8
</ref> [[Unrestricted admin mode]] is required.

== the device is busy ==
Kernel parameter {{CodeSelect|code=bdev_allow_write_mounted=0}} might need to be removed. See [[Grub|grub bootloader Configuration Changes]]. <ref>
https://forums.kicksecure.com/t/veracrypt-unable-to-decrypt-or-mount-any-volume-it-says-that-the-device-is-busy/1448
</ref>

